data.description: This move-in-ready, rustic ranch home is looking for a new owner! Old country charm meets modern amenities in the large, open kitchen. The family room boasts plenty of natural light and a wood-burning fireplace. Each bedroom has an ensuite bathroom. The oversized laundry room will help make doing laundry a breeze. The sunroom overlooks the sprawling backyard. Outside details an oversized porch and several outbuildings that make for great storage space. Get your offers in today!
